  "description": "<p><strong>据国外媒体报道，《阿凡达》导演詹姆斯·卡梅隆（James Cameron）对好莱坞依赖3D技术提出批评，并指出今年到目前为止最高收入的两部电影《钢铁侠3》和《超人：钢铁之躯》并不需要使用该种格式。</strong>卡梅隆在2009年推出的大热电影《阿凡达》开创了电影使用3D效果的先河，他日前在墨西哥城的Tag DF art大会上表示好莱坞“没有合适地使用3D技术”。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e6a1546/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244062.htm&amp;t=%E3%80%8A%E9%98%BF%E5%87%A1%E8%BE%BE%E3%80%8B%E5%AF%BC%E6%BC%94%E5%8D%A1%E6%A2%85%E9%9A%86%EF%BC%9A%E5%A5%BD%E8%8E%B1%E5%9D%9E%E6%BB%A5%E7%94%A83D%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244062.htm&amp;t=%E3%80%8A%E9%98%BF%E5%87%A1%E8%BE%BE%E3%80%8B%E5%AF%BC%E6%BC%94%E5%8D%A1%E6%A2%85%E9%9A%86%EF%BC%9A%E5%A5%BD%E8%8E%B1%E5%9D%9E%E6%BB%A5%E7%94%A83D%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244062.htm&amp;t=%E3%80%8A%E9%98%BF%E5%87%A1%E8%BE%BE%E3%80%8B%E5%AF%BC%E6%BC%94%E5%8D%A1%E6%A2%85%E9%9A%86%EF%BC%9A%E5%A5%BD%E8%8E%B1%E5%9D%9E%E6%BB%A5%E7%94%A83D%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244062.htm&amp;t=%E3%80%8A%E9%98%BF%E5%87%A1%E8%BE%BE%E3%80%8B%E5%AF%BC%E6%BC%94%E5%8D%A1%E6%A2%85%E9%9A%86%EF%BC%9A%E5%A5%BD%E8%8E%B1%E5%9D%9E%E6%BB%A5%E7%94%A83D%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=