  "description": "<p>智能手机用户一定都知道，免费应用虽说不收钱，但大部分都会在应用中显示广告。据安全反病毒企业Bitdefender所说，我们其实根本就不知道这些应 用的阴险狡诈及其从我们这里获得了多少利益。<strong>Bitdefender最新的一份报告中，提及免费应用实际上就相当于间谍软件，因为用户一旦安装这些免费应用就面临私人 信息被窃取的风险。</strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e6a1545/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244061.htm&amp;t=%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%A1%EF%BC%9A%E5%A4%A7%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E4%BC%9A%E7%AA%83%E5%8F%96%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E9%9A%90%E7%A7%81%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244061.htm&amp;t=%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%A1%EF%BC%9A%E5%A4%A7%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E4%BC%9A%E7%AA%83%E5%8F%96%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E9%9A%90%E7%A7%81%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244061.htm&amp;t=%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%A1%EF%BC%9A%E5%A4%A7%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E4%BC%9A%E7%AA%83%E5%8F%96%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E9%9A%90%E7%A7%81%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244061.htm&amp;t=%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%A1%EF%BC%9A%E5%A4%A7%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E4%BC%9A%E7%AA%83%E5%8F%96%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E9%9A%90%E7%A7%81%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/s